    <title>Hexo博客的搭建（受苦）之旅</title>
    <link href="http://7eaf.github.io/2020/09/13/HEXO/"/>
    <id>http://7eaf.github.io/2020/09/13/HEXO/</id>
    <published>2020-09-13T13:17:18.821Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-13T17:57:27.175Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/7eaf/photo/master/img/www.acg.gy_20.jpg"/> <a id="more"></a>这里用到的是win10系统<h2 id="前期准备"><a href="#前期准备" class="headerlink" title="前期准备"></a>前期准备</h2><p>1.安装Node.js环境：hexo基于这个框架<br>   下载地址: <a href="http://nodejs.cn/download/">http://nodejs.cn/download/</a><br>安装成功后win+r  输入cmd调出控制板面 输入以下代码</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ node -v <span class="comment">#查看node版本</span></span><br><span class="line">$ npm -v <span class="comment">#查看npm版本</span></span><br><span class="line">$ npm install -g cnpm --registry=http://registry.npm.taobao.org <span class="comment">#安装淘宝的cnpm 管理器</span></span><br><span class="line">$ cnpm -v <span class="comment">#查看cnpm版本</span></span><br><span class="line">$ cnpm install -g hexo-cli <span class="comment">#安装hexo框架</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo -v <span class="comment">#查看hexo版本</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Hexo安装"><a href="#Hexo安装" class="headerlink" title="Hexo安装"></a>Hexo安装</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-cli -g <span class="comment">#全局安装</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo-v <span class="comment">#查看hexo版本</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建本地博客站点"><a href="#创建本地博客站点" class="headerlink" title="创建本地博客站点"></a>创建本地博客站点</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ mkdir blog <span class="comment">#创建blog目录</span></span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> blog <span class="comment">#进入blog目录</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init <span class="comment">#生成博客 初始化博客</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s <span class="comment">#启动本地博客服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复制<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> 进入浏览器进行访问<br>至此，hexo项目搭建成功</p><h2 id="将项目部署至远端服务器"><a href="#将项目部署至远端服务器" class="headerlink" title="将项目部署至远端服务器"></a>将项目部署至远端服务器</h2><p>这里可以选择gitee和github 当然你有更好的可以选择别的 这里只说这两个 部署至github或者gitee可以不需要你购买服务器<br>因为墙的关系将项目部署至gittee各方面速度会比github快很多</p><h3 id="github"><a href="#github" class="headerlink" title="github"></a>github</h3><p>(这年头应该都有GitHub账号的吧)<br>在自己账号里面新建一个仓库<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/7eaf/photo/master/img/(D%60(%7EA6G%5D8ZFUT19%600N%7D4ER.png"/><br>这里仓库名与GitHub用户名一致</p><h3 id="在项目根目录下安装git部署插件"><a href="#在项目根目录下安装git部署插件" class="headerlink" title="在项目根目录下安装git部署插件"></a>在项目根目录下安装git部署插件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="修改全局配置文件"><a href="#修改全局配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改全局配置文件"></a>修改全局配置文件</h3><p>在项目的根目录中打开全局配置文件 _config.yml,在代码最下面，修改如下内容</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: 仓库URL地址</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br><span class="line">``` </span><br><span class="line">随后回到cmd版面输入如下命令</span><br><span class="line">``` bash</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">&quot;xxx&quot;</span> <span class="comment">#xxx为注册GitHub时的邮箱</span></span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">&quot;xxx&quot;</span> <span class="comment">#xxx为当前GitHub的用户名</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo cl <span class="comment">#清理</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g <span class="comment">#生成</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d <span class="comment">#部署</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署成功即可使用<a href="https://yourgithubname.github.io/">https://YourGithubName.github.io/</a> 打开你的博客</p><h3 id="gitee"><a href="#gitee" class="headerlink" title="gitee"></a>gitee</h3><p>步骤与github基本没什么区别<br>1.注册gitee账号<br>2.新建仓库<br>3.更改配置文件 然后部署<br>4.在部署完成后打开 Gitee Pages 静态网页托管服务 此后每次重新部署都要重载此服务<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/7eaf/photo/master/img/gitee.png"/></p>]]></content>
    
    
